-- E1a: a SINGLE-clause top-level function with a NON-variable parameter pattern
-- (a tuple `(a, b)`).  Confirms the fn half of gap #4 — `emitFn` now routes a
-- non-`allPVar` single clause through the decision-tree path, where the tuple
-- pattern binds `a`/`b` via `bindPattern` in the leaf, instead of panicking on
